App Store Description - ENGLISH
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A pure-skill game, no in-app purchases, no paid version! 

Kim felt he was too fat, so he decided to go running to lose weight. 
The problem is that on the way, he ran into some monsters! 
Now it's your task to help Kim to avoid the monsters and return home safely (and thin;). 

Developed and idealized by Igor Silva. 

